"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"### Broadcast Transaction\\n\\nThe `Broadcast Transaction` method is used to send a transaction to the network for processing.\\n\\nThe key parameters include the transaction itself and the mode of broadcasting, which is optional and defaults to synchronous broadcasting mode.\\n\\n#### Method Declaration\\n\\n:::code-group\\n\\n```python [Python]\\nasync def broadcast(self, transaction: Tx, mode=BroadcastMode.BROADCAST_MODE_SYNC)\\n```\\n\\n```typescript [TypeScript]\\nasync sendSignedTransaction(\\n    signedTransaction: Uint8Array,\\n): Promise<BroadcastTxAsyncResponse | BroadcastTxSyncResponse | IndexedTx>\\n```\\n\\n```rust [Rust]\\npub async fn broadcast_transaction(\\n    &mut self,\\n    tx_raw: Raw,\\n) -> Result<TxHash, NodeError>\\n```\\n\\n```url [API]\\n\\n```\\n\\n:::\\n\\n:::details[Unification Plan]\\n:::\\n\\n#### Parameters\\n\\n| Parameter     | Location | Type            | Required | Description                                                        |\\n| ------------- | -------- | --------------- | -------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------ |\\n| `transaction` | query    | [Tx]            | true     | The transaction to broadcast.                                      |\\n| `mode`        | query    | [BroadcastMode] | false    | The broadcast mode. Defaults to BroadcastMode.BROADCAST_MODE_SYNC. |\\n\\n:::\\n\\n#### Response\\n\\n| Status | Meaning       | Schema   |                                       |\\n| ------ | ------------- | -------- | ------------------------------------- |\\n| `200`  | [OK]          | [TxHash] |                                       |\\n| `400`  | [Bad Request] |          | The request was malformed or invalid. |\\n| `404`  | [Not Found]   |          | The transaction was not found.        |\\n\\nExamples: [Rust]\\n\\n[Rust]: https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients/blob/3e8c7e1b960291b7ef273962d374d9934a5c4d33/v4-client-rs/client/examples/withdraw_other.rs#L71\\n[Tx]: /types/tx\\n[BroadcastMode]: /types/broadcast_mode\\n[OK]: /types/ok\\n[TxHash]: /types/tx_hash\\n[Bad Request]: /types/bad-request\\n[Not Found]: /types/not-found\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/node-client/private/broadcast_transaction#broadcast-transaction\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>The <code>Broadcast Transaction</code> method is used to send a transaction to the network for processing.</p>\\n<p>The key parameters include the transaction itself and the mode of broadcasting, which is optional and defaults to synchronous broadcasting mode.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/node-client/private/broadcast_transaction.mdx#broadcast-transaction\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nThe Broadcast Transaction method is used to send a transaction to the network for processing.\\nThe key parameters include the transaction itself and the mode of broadcasting, which is optional and defaults to synchronous broadcasting mode.\\n\",\"title\":\"Broadcast Transaction\",\"titles\":[null,null]},{\"href\":\"/node-client/private/broadcast_transaction#method-declaration\",\"html\":\"\\n<div class=\\\"code-group\\\"><div data-title=\\\"Python\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"Python\\\" data-lang=\\\"python\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">async</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> def</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\"> broadcast</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(self, transaction: Tx, mode</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">=</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">BroadcastMode.</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\">BROADCAST_MODE_SYNC</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">)</span></span></code></pre></div><div data-title=\\\"TypeScript\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"TypeScript\\\" data-lang=\\\"typescript\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">async </span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\">sendSignedTransaction</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    signedTransaction: Uint8Array,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">): </span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\">Promise</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">BroadcastTxAsyncResponse </span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">|</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> BroadcastTxSyncResponse </span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">|</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> IndexedTx</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><div data-title=\\\"Rust\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"Rust\\\" data-lang=\\\"rust\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">pub</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> async</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> fn</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\"> broadcast_transaction</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">    &amp;mut</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> self</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    tx_raw</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">:</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\"> Raw</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">-&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\"> Result</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">TxHash</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">, </span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">NodeError</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><div data-title=\\\"API\\\"><pre><code class=\\\"language-url\\\"></code></pre></div></div>\\n<details><summary>Unification Plan</summary></details>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/node-client/private/broadcast_transaction.mdx#method-declaration\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nasync def broadcast(self, transaction: Tx, mode=BroadcastMode.BROADCAST_MODE_SYNC)async sendSignedTransaction(\\n    signedTransaction: Uint8Array,\\n): Promise&lt;BroadcastTxAsyncResponse | BroadcastTxSyncResponse | IndexedTx&gt;pub async fn broadcast_transaction(\\n    &amp;mut self,\\n    tx_raw: Raw,\\n) -&gt; Result&lt;TxHash, NodeError&gt;\\nUnification Plan\\n\",\"title\":\"Method Declaration\",\"titles\":[null,null,\"Broadcast Transaction\"]},{\"href\":\"/node-client/private/broadcast_transaction#parameters\",\"html\":\"\\n<table><thead><tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Location</th><th>Type</th><th>Required</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>transaction</code></td><td>query</td><td><a href=\\\"/types/tx\\\">Tx</a></td><td>true</td><td>The transaction to broadcast.</td></tr><tr><td><code>mode</code></td><td>query</td><td><a href=\\\"/types/broadcast_mode\\\">BroadcastMode</a></td><td>false</td><td>The broadcast mode. Defaults to BroadcastMode.BROADCAST_MODE_SYNC.</td></tr></tbody></table>\\n<p>:::</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/node-client/private/broadcast_transaction.mdx#parameters\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nParameterLocationTypeRequiredDescriptiontransactionqueryTxtrueThe transaction to broadcast.modequeryBroadcastModefalseThe broadcast mode. Defaults to BroadcastMode.BROADCAST_MODE_SYNC.\\n:::\\n\",\"title\":\"Parameters\",\"titles\":[null,null,\"Broadcast Transaction\"]},{\"href\":\"/node-client/private/broadcast_transaction#response\",\"html\":\"\\n<table><thead><tr><th>Status</th><th>Meaning</th><th>Schema</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>200</code></td><td><a href=\\\"/types/ok\\\">OK</a></td><td><a href=\\\"/types/tx_hash\\\">TxHash</a></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><code>400</code></td><td><a href=\\\"/types/bad-request\\\">Bad Request</a></td><td></td><td>The request was malformed or invalid.</td></tr><tr><td><code>404</code></td><td><a href=\\\"/types/not-found\\\">Not Found</a></td><td></td><td>The transaction was not found.</td></tr></tbody></table>\\n<p>Examples: <a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients/blob/3e8c7e1b960291b7ef273962d374d9934a5c4d33/v4-client-rs/client/examples/withdraw_other.rs#L71\\\">Rust</a></p>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/node-client/private/broadcast_transaction.mdx#response\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nStatusMeaningSchema200OKTxHash400Bad RequestThe request was malformed or invalid.404Not FoundThe transaction was not found.\\nExamples: Rust\",\"title\":\"Response\",\"titles\":[null,null,\"Broadcast Transaction\"]}]}}"
